  "id": "019d328d-8c8e-7171-8e32-58b460f489d9",
  "content": "# corvia-adapter-agent-teams: Brainstorm Decisions\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-28\n**Doc:** docs/decisions/2026-03-28-adapter-agent-teams-brainstorm.md\n\nFive open questions were brainstormed with deep independent analysis. Key decisions:\n\n## Q1: Capture Before Cleanup\n**Decision:** Hook-based incremental capture (primary) + periodic scan (fallback).\nHooks (TaskCreated, TaskCompleted, teammate SessionEnd) write to staging at `~/.corvia/staging/agent-teams/{team-name}/`. Staging survives cleanup. Skip TeammateIdle (too noisy). Matches claude-sessions adapter pattern exactly.\n\n## Q2: Agent ID Correlation\n**Decision:** Use teammate name as link key (names are unique, used for message routing). SessionStart hook writes mapping file at `~/.claude/sessions/.team-mapping` with `{session_id}\\t{team_name}\\t{agent_name}`. CorrelationIndex tries: explicit mapping > agent name in prompt > temporal overlap. Research spike needed to verify available env vars.\n\n## Q3: Incremental Capture\n**Decision:** Hybrid. TaskCreated/TaskCompleted hooks capture incrementally. Teammate SessionEnd does final sweep (inbox, config, remaining tasks). All file reads synchronous inside hook (files may be deleted before async processing). Skip TeammateIdle for capture.\n\n## Q4: Message Chunking\n**Decision:** Task-grouped chunking primary (one entry per task discussion, 5-15 entries per session). Optional LLM extraction secondary pass (decisions, findings, disagreements via classify-queue). 6-month estimate: 1,500-4,500 entries.\n\n## Q5: Subagent Attribution\n**Decision:** Rely on existing `spawned_by` chain from claude-sessions adapter. No team metadata on subagents. No direct team-to-subagent edges. Strictly hierarchical graph: team -> has_member -> teammate -> spawned_by <- subagent. Three hops within max_depth:3 default. Zero modifications to claude-sessions adapter needed.\n\n## Blocker\nOne research spike needed before RFC: spin up Agent Teams and dump env vars from teammate SessionStart hook to verify what identity information is accessible.\n",
